加载。” <em>The Verge</em>将最初故事的截图上传到了<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://imgur.com/a/fg8mxgy">Imgur</a> 。</p><p>该文章的作者仅被列为“Microsoft Travel”，这表明真实的人可能没有参与其创作。 Microsoft Start 的“关于我们”网页声称，它对算法使用“人工监督”，“梳理我们合作伙伴发送的数十万条内容”，以帮助公司“了解新鲜度、类别、主题类型、观点内容等维度”以及潜在的流行度并根据用户的喜好进行发布。”据报道，这家 Windows 制造商在 2020 年<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.windowscentral.com/microsoft-replacing-dozens-journalists-ai-msn">解雇了</a>该部门约 50 名记者，同时转向人工智能生成新闻。</p><p>微软并不是第一家过度热衷于使用人工智能创建的内容的公司。今年年初， <em>CNET</em>发表了<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/cnet-corrected-41-of-its-77-ai-written-articles-201519489.html">多篇由人工智能撰写的错误百出的金融解释文章</a>。最近， <em>Gizmodo</em>的母公司 G/O Media 在网站上<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2023/07/08/gizmodo-ai-errors-star-wars/">发布了</a>一篇由人工智能撰写（也充满错误）的《星球大战》文章，副编辑 James Whitbrook 称这篇文章“令人尴尬、无法发表、不尊重”。随着<em>美联社</em>对人工智能辅助新闻报道<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/new-ap-guidelines-lay-the-groundwork-for-ai-assisted-newsrooms-201009363.html">持谨慎态度</a>，其他媒体——包括微软的新闻出版部门——似乎更愿意从完全由人工智能撰写的文章中获利，从而在事后清除不可避免的残骸。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-retracts-ai-writing-article-advising-tourists-to-visit-a-food-bank-on-an-empty-stomach-182701884 .html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-retracts-ai-written-article-advising-tourists-to-visit-a-food-bank-on-an-empty-stomach-182701884.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 71c32130-0fb1-45b1-b1a6-5e73e652403f</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 18 Aug 2023 18:27:01 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692383632</ingested><modified> 2023-08-18T18:34:07+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/dbf65270-3df1-11ee-9eff-e851ca949b60" width="1800"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/dbf65270-3df1-11ee-9eff-e851ca949b60" width="1800"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Ottawa Food Bank]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A woman stands in front of a red wall that reads, "Ottawa Food Bank" with its French translation below.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Ottawa Food Bank]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best smart scales for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>数据在任何战斗中都是有用的工具，尤其是当您选择向腰围发起战争以变得更健康时。早在 2007 年，我买了一个非常便宜的体重秤，并绘制了自己的图表，以便记录在大学度过了艰难的一年后我的体重下降情况。我认为，虽然 2007 年我不会对自己的健身之旅感到满意，但他会喜欢这个过程完全自动化且价格实惠的事实。因此，请允许我带您（和他）选择最好的智能体重秤，以帮助您实现行为改变和改善整体健康。</p><h2>安全</h2><p>称体重是有充分理由的，但你的自我价值不应该由双脚之间出现的数字来定义。如果你想改变你的体型，随着你的腰围下降，这个数字可能会上升，因为肌肉比脂肪重。剑桥大学公共卫生教学主任安妮·斯威夫特博士表示，“过于频繁地称重可能会导致你专注于日常的微小波动，而不是一段时间内的总体趋势。”斯威夫特补充道，“有时最好关注衣服是否合身，或者你的感觉如何，而不是你的体重。”</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> （ <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26742706/">2016 年</a>的一项荟萃​​分析发现，自我称重可能会产生一些负面的心理影响。然而， <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.ahajournals.org/doi/10.1161/circ.138.suppl_1.10962">2018 年的一项研究</a>表示，定期称重和加速减肥之间可能存在正相关关系。这可能是一个雷区，并且我敦促您真正照顾好自己，并记住成功不会在一夜之间发生。）</p><h2>智能秤需要注意什么</h2><h3>重量</h3><p>能够称量您体重的体重秤可能是首要要求，对吗？需要记住的一件事是，通过所有这些测量，这些数字不会像经过校准的临床量表那么准确。因此，最好关注随着时间的推移整体体重上升或下降的趋势，而不是孤立的数字。</p><h3>连接性</h3><p>大多数电子秤会通过蓝牙连接到您的手机，或者连接到您家中的 WiFi 网络，您应该提前制定常规称重程序。许多低端纯蓝牙秤只会在您的手机存在时记录您的体重，并且不会保留本地记录。这意味着，如果您经常将手机留在家里的浴室外面，您可能会丢失当天的统计数据。另一方面，WiFi 秤将您的统计数据发布到服务器，让您可以从任何兼容设备访问它们。但您需要注意，如果信息被泄露，您的隐私将面临很小的风险。</p><h3>骨密度</h3><p>您的骨骼越强壮，骨折和骨质疏松症的风险就越小，随着年龄的增长，您应该牢记这一点。临床骨密度测试使用低功率 X 射线，但高端秤可以在您自己的浴室中提供近似值。这些骨量测试会通过您的脚传递小电流，测量电流完成行程时的阻力。骨骼、脂肪和肌肉提供的阻力都是不同的，您的体重秤可以识别差异。</p><h3>身体脂肪百分比和肌肉质量</h3><p>脂肪和肌肉是我们身体的必要组成部分，但任何一种过多都会产生问题。与骨密度非常相似，体重秤可以使用生物电阻抗分析 (BIA) 来确定您的身体脂肪和肌肉质量百分比。该测量测试您的身体抵抗通过您身体的电信号的能力。 （根据粗略的经验法则，脂肪和肌肉的比例应为 30/70%，但请咨询医疗专业人士，了解针对您自己的身体和医疗需求的具体数字。）</p><h3>体重指数</h3><p>许多体重秤都提供 BMI 计算，而且很容易做到，因为您只需在设定的图表线上绘制身高和体重。然而，体重指数是一个有问题的测量方法，批评者称其<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2930234/">过于简单化</a>，而且往往<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.pennmedicine.org/news/news-releases/2013/august/obesitymortality-paradox-demon">具有很大的误导性</a>。不幸的是，它也是最常见的临床身体指标之一，医疗专业人员将使用它来对您的护理做出判断。</p><h3>脉搏波速度</h3><p>法国健康科技公司 Withings 已经在其旗舰秤上提供脉搏波速度 (PWV) 服务一段时间了，不过监管方面的担忧意味着该服务已被撤回一段时间。它是动脉僵硬度的测量值，可作为心血管风险和其他健康状况的标志。我听说过一些轶事报道称，脉搏波速度量表已将人们送往医生那里，他们发现自己接近心脏事件。值得一提的是，与所有这些技术一样，<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32168728/">尽管对这些系统的准确性进行了积极的</a>研究，但仍然有限。</p><h3>展示</h3><p>与其说是一个规格，不如说是一个说明，智能秤的显示屏范围从预印的 LCD 或数字点阵布局到彩色屏幕。在高端，您的体重秤显示屏可以向您显示体重趋势图和其他重要统计数据，甚至可以告诉您当天的天气。如果您是近视眼，并计划早上第一件事就是称体重，然后找到眼镜/隐形眼镜，请选择大而清晰、高对比度的显示屏。</p><h3>应用程序和订阅</h3><p>您将花费大部分时间通过其配套应用程序查看您的健康数据，因此拥有一款好的应用程序至关重要。这包括清晰、干净的布局和强大的工具来可视化您的进度并分析您的数据以寻找可以改进的地方。鉴于您在尝试该应用程序之前通常不需要购买任何东西，因此值得测试一两个，看看您是否喜欢它。</p><p>一些公司还提供高级订阅，解锁其他功能（包括见解和指导）以配合您的硬件。 Fitbit 和 Withings 都提供这些服务，您可能会觉得每个月的额外投资都是值得的。</p><h3>数据可移植性</h3><p>连续多年使用相同的秤或应用程序平台意味着您将积累大量个人数据。当您将来选择移动平台时，您有权或应该将这些数据转移给其他提供商。然而，数据可移植性是一个雷区，不同的平台提供截然不同的选项，使得迁移到其他地方很容易（或很难）。</p><p>本综述中的所有设备都允许您将数据导出到 .CSV 文件，然后您可以根据需要进行处理。导入这些信息比较棘手，Withings 和 Garmin 允许导入，而 Omron、小米、Eufy 和 Fitbit 则不那么容易。 （同时，与 Apple Health 交互的应用程序可以<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N1cHBvcnQuYXBwbGUuY29tL2VuLWdiL2d1aWRlL2lwaG9uZS9pcGg1ZWRlNThjM2QvaW9zIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJiMmFmMmE1Ni1kZTk5LTRhNDMtOGJkOS1kNWU1NzY4MjVlODMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAZCtZe_M4AKLG6lYTWvN8T0ow_5B8_ackKhQ43NQGnWK&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-gb%2Fguide%2Fiphone%2Fiph5ede58c3d%2Fios">将您的所有健康数据输出</a>到 .XML 文件中。）</p><h3>力量</h3><p>这不是一个大问题，但值得记住的是，每个秤要么使用一次性电池（最常见的是 4xAAA），要么使用自己的内置电池组。遗憾的是，我们所有的智能秤都使用电池，从而增加了秤的使用寿命的环境和财务成本。对于价格低于 100 美元的体重秤来说，这几乎是可以原谅的，但这种情况甚至适用于最高端的型号。当你在设备上花费的钱超过这个数字时，缺少充电电池确实会让人感觉非常非常便宜。</p><h2>我们测试的智能体重秤</h2><p>在本指南中，我测试了主要制造商的六种秤：</p><h3> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZ_n5jXiqBRDOptIAu84EmySDSs5Qwbio4LWHd3rYib8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FXiaomi-Composition-Bluetooth-Statistics-Smartphone%2Fdp%2FB07XNHW2JH">Mi（小米）身体成分秤 2</a> （29.99 美元） </h3><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/5682ca60-7704-11ed-b7ef-e04eaf660ec8" alt="小米体重秤的库存图片" data-uuid="836d3451-4913-35c9-ab33-aef32e3c800e"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">小米</div></figure><p>我们最便宜的型号，小米/米的身体成分秤 2 是你能得到的最简单的，它显示了这一点。通常需要很长时间才能锁定您的体重，一旦锁定，您就必须深入研究 Zepp Life 品牌的应用程序才能查看您的额外数据。但它的基本功能无可挑剔，它提供有限的重量和身体成分，价格还低于麦当劳四人份的价格。</p><h3> <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdedVAmboPWBTWdpUHTI7X3sMt__hDB1_bW8Ef-Yq4yH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFitbit-FB203BK-Bluetooth-Digital-Weight%2Fdp%2FB07VV6GKDS">Fitbit Aira Air</a> （49.95 美元） </h3><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/72f09f60-7704-11ed-afdf-974ce8437af6" alt="Fitbit 的 Aria Air 体重秤图片" data-uuid="f28a6a3b-ca2f-31ba-8c83-9e5afab6ac24"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">菲比特</div></figure><p>Fitbit（现已成为 Google 的一部分）是美国健身追踪器的家喻户晓的名字，对吧？如果不是，那么它必须至少与它有一半同义。 Aria Air 是该公司的精简秤，可提供您的体重和其他一些健康指标，但您可以相信 Fitbit 的基本功能是正确的。更不用说购买 Fitbit 产品的大部分原因是为了利用其健身应用程序。</p><h3> <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQkVA5ofcfXgBHkGUcOOXsKMlPTtBM0pu-dOKiWpfQM9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Feufy-Bathroom-Bluetooth-Measurements-Including%2Fdp%2FB09NHR4NX7%2F">Anker Eufy 智能秤 P2 Pro</a> （79.99 美元） </h3><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/8b138440-7704-11ed-b67f-a253630e349c" alt="Eufy 的 P2 Pro 智能体重秤图片" data-uuid="ebcb8171-9cdf-3cfb-ac5a-f19891d7b618"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">尤菲/安克</div></figure><p>Eufy 的 Smart Scale P2 Pro 有很多值得称赞的地方——价格、整体外观和感觉（这是一个时髦的套件）以及它提供的功能。它提供一系列深入的测量，包括身体脂肪、肌肉质量、水分重量、身体脂肪质量和骨质量，以及计算心率和基础代谢率（您需要摄入的卡路里量）等数据完全不改变体重的一天）全部来自其应用程序内部。事实上，在友好的图形下面，该秤提供了大量统计数据和数据，我认为，这些数据应该为您提供有关如何改善生活方式的更多指导。</p><p>发布前不久，Eufy 的母公司 Anker 被认定在其产品的安全性方面误导了用户和媒体。其 Eufy 品牌的安全摄像头被发现允许第三方在线访问流媒体，该公司称该摄像头不会在本地网络之外播放视频。因此，虽然我们赞扬了 Eufy 智能体重秤的自身功能，但我们不能不郑重地推荐它。</p><h3> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASi75Tjd0SgYfb-B9rkmhg6WTzW1HyxGlJthfPDFT3f3&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOmron-Composition-Monitor-Bluetooth-Connectivity%2Fdp%2FB07WHMBH8K">欧姆龙 BCM-500 身体成分和体重秤，带蓝牙</a>（89.99 美元） </h3><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/b5bb7810-7704-11ed-9bfd-fa2c08b531c4" alt="欧姆龙500系列秤图片" data-uuid="8c2436d8-674a-3110-b6f3-3748014ca6ec"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">欧姆龙</div></figure><p>鉴于其在制造实际医疗设备中的作用，您知道欧姆龙产品会带来什么。坚固、可靠、坚固、坚固（查看字典以获取更多同义词）可靠的套件。没有表现出浪漫或兴奋，但你可以相信，无论它可能多么无趣，它都会完成所讨论的工作，并且用户友好。硬件有限，应用程序有限，但它肯定（再次检查同义词）是稳定的。</p><p>开玩笑吧，欧姆龙的 Connect 应用程序非常简单，因为它充当了许多产品的界面。滚动到“体重”页面，您将获得体重和 BMI 读数，如果您设定了健身目标，您还可以看到要达到该目标还需要走多远。您还可以切换到查看趋势图，该图再次提供最基本的可视化效果。</p><h3> <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9HYXJtaW4tV2lyZWxlc3MtQ29ubmVjdGl2aXR5LU1lYXN1cmUtTXVzY2xlL2RwL0IwOEpRUFJOVlg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tY3ItMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImIyYWYyYTU2LWRlOTktNGE0My04YmQ5LWQ1ZTU3NjgyNWU4MyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZHC0N0m24_KjtwpGTvy7iEUBJ4c3t1O5sr-aJEhmGpA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGarmin-Wireless-Connectivity-Measure-Muscle%2Fdp%2FB08JQPRNVX">Garmin Index S2</a> （149.99 美元） </h3><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/cbe09120-7704-11ed-96f7-43fa6701cbfb" alt="Garmin Index S2 智能体重秤图片" data-uuid="4cf275f1-c12f-3c69-9d86-e251b88a70b3"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">佳明</div></figure><p>Garmin 拥有自己的相当庞大的健身生态系统，因此，如果您已经是这个世界的一部分，那么它的智能浴室秤是理所当然的。一方面，该秤是最容易使用、最豪华的秤之一，具有彩色屏幕和时尚的设计。我也非常喜欢该体重秤向您提供的大量数据——您可以看到一个全彩图表，记录您的体重进展情况，以及它详细跟踪的各种指标。如果说有什么缺点的话，那就是 Garmin 的设置不太适合你，因为它适合认真的健身人士，而不是新手。</p><h3> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Withings;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=d3b3fb13-488a-4810-a40f-ee84ae8f2918&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Withings&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJkM2IzZmIxMy00ODhhLTQ4MTAtYTQwZi1lZTg0YWU4ZjI5MTgiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud2l0aGluZ3MuY29tL3VzL2VuL2JvZHktY29tcCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYjJhZjJhNTYtZGU5OS00YTQzLThiZDktZDVlNTc2ODI1ZTgzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAc8X9rt-aX4wH02_myPQh5OPGfGfhGCp4LvKeEkxPEmJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.withings.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fbody-comp">Withings Body Comp</a> （209.95 美元） </h3><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/e0ff36b0-7704-11ed-bbd7-35a0b488360f" alt="Withings Body Comp 的图片" data-uuid="8db1f98c-eef3-334e-93fe-97c1a32c0318"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">威辛斯</div></figure><p>在最高端，Withings 的旗舰产品 Body Comp 非常奢华，而且价格昂贵，我认为这个数字对于浴室秤来说“太多”了。然而，只要花点钱，您就能获得相当全面的体重、体脂百分比、血管年龄、脉搏波速度和皮肤电活动的详细信息。它的单色点阵显示屏可能不像 Garmin 那样漂亮，但刷新速度相当快，而且感觉与硬件的整体时尚外观非常一致。如果说有什么缺点的话，那就是他们放弃了 Withings Body Cardio（它的前旗舰产品，如果在本指南的参数范围内，我会推荐的一款出色的体重秤）中使用的可充电电池，转而使用 AAA 电池。当你在秤上花费这么多时，让我感觉非常小气。</p><h2>最便宜的智能体重秤：Fitbit Aria Air、 <strong>Mi Body Composition Scale 2</strong> </h2><p><core-commerce id="55f3e395d8e045399b07c9d7af9846d2" data-type="product-list"></p><p><core-commerce id="d0a1eeed3de14400a197c1ab415d1558" data-type="product-list"></p><p>对于最佳预算智能体重秤来说，它在低端市场非常有竞争力， <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZ_n5jXiqBRDOptIAu84EmySDSs5Qwbio4LWHd3rYib8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FXiaomi-Composition-Bluetooth-Statistics-Smartphone%2Fdp%2FB07XNHW2JH">小米</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdedVAmboPWBTWdpUHTI7X3sMt__hDB1_bW8Ef-Yq4yH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFitbit-FB203BK-Bluetooth-Digital-Weight%2Fdp%2FB07VV6GKDS">Fitbit</a>以非常低的价格提供了截然不同的产品。 Fitbit 的体重秤的功能要少得多，但与更便宜的竞争对手相比，其制造质量更好，速度更快、更可靠。至关重要的是，它还利用了 Fitbit 应用程序，该应用程序精致且易于使用，提供干净、易于理解的可视化效果。</p><p>与此同时，小米提供了体重和一些基本的身体成分测量数据，尽管这些额外的数据仅在应用程序内可视化。从数据的角度来看，小米有优势，但它的配套应用程序——以前的 Mi Fit，现在的品牌为 Zepp Life——很糟糕。尽管我对小米的准确性没有任何疑虑，但每次称重的延迟时间也让小米有很多不足之处。</p><p>当我还是个孩子的时候，抱怨一些事情时，我奶奶会说：“听着，你要么乘坐头等舱步行，要么乘坐三等舱乘车。” Fitbit 的体重秤正是一流骑行的定义——精致、敏捷，并配有世界一流的应用程序。与此同时，小米手机的性价比更高，而且收费更低，但硬件和软件都缺乏任何改进。因此，您选择乘坐头等舱步行还是三等舱乘坐取决于您。</p><h2>对于想要功能（并且不担心安全性）的人来说最好的秤：Eufy 的 P2 Pro</h2><p><core-commerce id="94d71cfa25df4515a885442682d0b1e9" data-type="product-list"></p><p>嗯，这是尴尬。在本指南发布前不久，有消息称<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQkVA5ofcfXgBHkGUcOOXsKMlPTtBM0pu-dOKiWpfQM9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Feufy-Bathroom-Bluetooth-Measurements-Including%2Fdp%2FB09NHR4NX7%2F">Eufy</a>正面临严重的安全问题。研究人员发现，其承诺安全的安全摄像头允许互联网用户使用 VLC 播放器访问流媒体。因此，我对 Eufy P2 Pro 的高度赞扬需要受到以下事实的影响：我们还不知道该公司在隐私和安全方面的承诺到底有多深入。</p><p>不幸的是，它的规模确实远远超出了这个级别的竞争对手，并且超出了我的预期。易用性是一回事，但应用程序中提供的度量数据的深度以及它呈现信息的方式非常棒。虽然我不认为 Eufy Life 应用程序比 Withings 一流的 Health Mate 等应用程序更好，但它确实提供了潜在体重观察者所需要的功能。</p><p>事实上，您可以通过点击两个按钮来获取大量的重要统计数据，这有助于您可视化您的进度，但列出所有内容（包括您的 BMR）的统计仪表板非常有用。如果你完全量化自我，理论上你可以通过每天早上查看这个东西来计算你每天的卡路里摄入量，以最精确的方式计算。</p><h2>最适合运动员的体重秤：Garmin Index S2</h2><p><core-commerce id="affb9482d05c466385eb81b42f862de2" data-type="product-list"></p><p>我非常偏爱<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9HYXJtaW4tV2lyZWxlc3MtQ29ubmVjdGl2aXR5LU1lYXN1cmUtTXVzY2xlL2RwL0IwOEpRUFJOVlg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tY3ItMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImIyYWYyYTU2LWRlOTktNGE0My04YmQ5LWQ1ZTU3NjgyNWU4MyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZHC0N0m24_KjtwpGTvy7iEUBJ4c3t1O5sr-aJEhmGpA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGarmin-Wireless-Connectivity-Measure-Muscle%2Fdp%2FB08JQPRNVX">Garmin 的 Index S2</a> ，但我也认为这是一种适合那些知道自己在做什么的人使用的秤。硬件方面几乎所有方面都非常到位，唯一的美中不足是彩色屏幕的刷新率较低。我无法形容看到显示屏以如此迟缓、未经打磨的方式刷新是多么令人沮丧，尤其是当你花了这么多钱的时候。但这是我唯一的抱怨，其余的硬件（和软件）在其他方面都非常完美。如果您希望设定目标来改变您的体型，这可能不适合您 – 这是您在每天计算基础代谢率后购买的体重秤。</p><h2>适合忧心忡忡的人的最佳体重秤：Withings Body Comp</h2><p><core-commerce id="9df2564d1e734471bb0e6c6373a5e3ca" data-type="product-list"></p><p>当然，如果您正在寻找一款能够满足您各种突发奇想和忧郁症冲动的机器，那么<a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Withings;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=d3b3fb13-488a-4810-a40f-ee84ae8f2918&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Withings&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJkM2IzZmIxMy00ODhhLTQ4MTAtYTQwZi1lZTg0YWU4ZjI5MTgiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud2l0aGluZ3MuY29tL3VzL2VuL2JvZHktY29tcCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYjJhZjJhNTYtZGU5OS00YTQzLThiZDktZDVlNTc2ODI1ZTgzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAc8X9rt-aX4wH02_myPQh5OPGfGfhGCp4LvKeEkxPEmJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.withings.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fbody-comp">Withings 的 Body Comp</a>就是您的最佳选择。从任何意义上来说，这都是一款奢华的秤，您应该欣赏这里展示的抛光和技术水平。除了电池之外，我已经说过，考虑到你在产品上投入了这么多钱，这是一种廉价而令人讨厌的省钱方式。</p><p>认为在规模上花费 200 美元是合理的人，特别是在食品和能源价格飙升的情况下，这一群体相当小。但如果你是那种已经不遗余力地控制自己身体的人，那么这可能是合理的“投资”。了解有关神经健康和动脉的所有额外信息是一个好处，但我们要明确一点，这并不是每个人的首选。天哪，即使您订阅了《Good Yachting》杂志，您也可能会重新考虑。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-scale-160033523.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-scale-160033523.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> b2af2a56-de99-4a43-8bd9-d5e576825e83</guid><dc:creator>丹尼尔·库珀</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 18 Aug 2023 18:00:20 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692381620</ingested><modified> 2023-08-18T18:00:38+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Daniel Cooper]]></category><media:content height="4160" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/e83a6d00-7af6-11ed-bffb-35bef259a819" width="6240"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4160" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/e83a6d00-7af6-11ed-bffb-35bef259a819" width="6240"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[PonyWang via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[woman weighing on scale to measure her weight]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[closeup of weighing on scale]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Lamborghini’s new all-electric concept car was inspired by spaceships]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>兰博基尼以解决许多中年危机而闻名， <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lamborghini-teases-a-fully-electric-supercar-ahead-of-its-august-18th-reveal-201059772.html">几天前在蒙特利汽车周上发布了一款新的电动概念车。</a>全电动兰博基尼 Lanzador 拥有各种高科技附加功能，其设计灵感实际上来自太空飞船。这款豪华旅行车 (GT) 具有大量信息娱乐功能，配有大型 Y 形中控台桥和用于进行调整的细长仪表板。</p><p>驾驶员还可以通过集成的“飞行员单元”即时访问气候控制和各种数字功能。该装置还允许通过该公司的 ANIMA 控制系统访问一系列驾驶模式。甚至还有可伸缩的显示器，可以向乘客传输有关速度、距离、气候、娱乐等的相关信息。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>至于设计，驾驶员和乘客坐在靠近地面的位置，就像在喷气式飞机中一样，并被中控台隔开。该公司表示，尽管车顶高度约为 1.5 米，但车内空间“出乎意料地宽敞”，进一步增加了汽车的低离地比例。后部空间可用于存放行李和其他必需品，前盖下方有一个隐藏式行李箱，提供更多存储选择。</p><p>设计确实很酷，但是所有这些内部速度增强功能又如何呢？ Lanzador 的每个车轴上都配备了高功率电动机，峰值功率超过一兆瓦。后轴配备带电子扭矩的全轮驱动装置，可改善转弯性能。兰博基尼表示，它全部由“新一代高性能电池”提供动力，并确保较长的行驶里程，但没有公布每次充电的实际里程。该公司还表示，该车的空气动力学设计应该会进一步增加实际行驶里程。</p><p>兰博基尼表示，虽然严格来说是一款概念车，但 Lanzador 不仅仅是“设计师和工程师的突发奇想”，它还提供了将于 2028 年开始推出的量产车的“具体预览”。为此，这里强调生态友好的设计材料，如美利奴羊毛、可持续鞣制皮革和再生碳。这也进一步证明该<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lamborghini-will-go-fully-electric-in-the-second-part-of-the-decade-114537409.html">公司认真考虑到 2030 年实现全电动化</a>。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/lamborghinis-new-all-electric-concept-car-was-inspired-by-spaceships-174550629.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/lamborghinis-new-all-electric-concept-car-was-inspired-by-spaceships-174550629.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 521cd479-0ff7-45d4-b5a7-43da2d2a63bd</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 18 Aug 2023 17:45:50 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692383927</ingested><modified> 2023-08-18T18:38:51+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Autos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="6336" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3e4e92d0-3df6-11ee-99ff-660303f36a0e" width="9504"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="6336" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3e4e92d0-3df6-11ee-99ff-660303f36a0e" width="9504"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Lamborghini]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Image of Lamborghini concept car.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Lamborghini Concept]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Fans are adapting 'Twin Peaks' into a PS1-style adventure game, and there's a demo]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>你可能已经看过<em>《双峰》</em>的原版很多遍，每次拿起一杯咖啡时都会感叹“该死的好咖啡”，但你有没有通过 FBI 特工戴尔·库珀的视角来体验这个故事呢？您很快就能通过视频游戏的魔力做到这一点。一家名为 Blue Rose Team 的法国小型开发商已经为<em>《双峰：黑夜》</em>做准备有一段时间了，它<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://blueroseteam.itch.io/twin-peaks-into-the-night"><ins>刚刚发布了这款粉丝制作的游戏的演示版</ins></a>。</p><p>画面复古，明显具有 PS1 风格，考虑到该剧于 1990 年首播，这是有道理的。游戏玩法看起来充满了探索，包括与镇上许多古怪居民的对话，尽管有一个生存恐怖元素让人想起原作<em>生化危机的</em>标题。这也是一个合适的设计选择，因为该剧让库珀特工对抗物理和超自然的敌人。你应该期待臭名昭著的独臂男子、混乱特工鲍勃、邪恶的前联邦调查局特工温德姆·厄尔的出现，当然还有大量的猫头鹰。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="af8d603268a7491d8958be5d599df51a"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nvii7t61BM4" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>除了游戏玩法之外，似乎还有一系列从节目本身中挑选出来的视频过场动画。周二发布的演示版记录了第一季中的事件，库珀抵达双峰并开始侦破当地青少年劳拉·帕尔默的谋杀案。该演示充满了怪异的怪癖和形而上的恐怖元素，这些元素使得 OG 节目在当时大受欢迎。</p><p>创作者已宣布该游戏在发布时将是免费的，因此这应该可以消除任何潜在的法律障碍。大卫·林奇 (David Lynch) 正忙着<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l21GFyOO8Ug"><ins>在 YouTube 或其他网站上做每日天气预报</ins></a>，所以他不会抱怨，但美国广播公司 (ABC) 和华纳兄弟并不像电影制片人/画家/冥想爱好者那么冷静。</p><p>目前还没有正式的发布日期，但演示版应该会让您忙碌一段时间。奇怪的是，这将是<em>《双峰》</em>视频游戏的第一部改编作品，尽管<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-12-09-twin-peaks-vr-trailer.html"><ins>VR 体验很短。</ins></a>尽管从未被正式改编，但该剧已经为许多游戏提供了灵感， <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/alan-wake-ii-stands-out-in-a-sea-of-sequels-140010178.html"><ins>从</ins><em><ins>《心灵杀手</ins></em><ins>》系列</ins></a>到鲜为人知的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.kotaku.com.au/2023/05/twin-peaks-co-creator-says-he-gave-some-ideas-for-links-awakening/"><em><ins>《塞尔达传说：林克的觉醒》</ins></em> <ins>。</ins></a>不用说， <em>《双峰：黑夜》</em>并没有深入探讨 Showtime 的<em>《双峰：归来》中的事件，</em>所以不要指望能控制吉姆·贝鲁什。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/fans-are-adapting-twin-peaks-into-a-ps1-style-adventure-game-and-theres-a-demo-163643462.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/fans-are-adapting-twin-peaks-into-a-ps1-style-adventure-game-and-theres-a-demo-163643462.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 2c7fb9fb-661f-4d21-8787-74b7df3b1b71</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 18 Aug 2023 16:36:43 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692376603</ingested><modified> 2023-08-18T16:36:47+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="600" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/32eefb50-3de2-11ee-b6ed-74410ebb3b17" width="800"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="600" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/32eefb50-3de2-11ee-b6ed-74410ebb3b17" width="800"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Blue Rose Team]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Title screen for 'Twin Peaks: Into the Night.']]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Twin Peaks Game]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Google Keep is finally adding version history]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>该公司的笔记应用程序<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/google-keep/"><ins>Google Keep</ins></a>正在获得一项期待已久的功能，不幸的是，该功能似乎尚未完全成熟。谷歌正在添加版本历史记录功能，这可以使您不必手动重新输入大量错误删除的文本。</p><p>根据<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://support.google.com/keep/answer/13820887?hl=en&amp;co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop&amp;oco=0"><ins>支持页面</ins></a>，该工具允许您下载包含以前版本的笔记和列表的文本文件。帮助文档指出，谷歌正在逐步向所有人推出该功能，因此它可能尚未为您提供。如果是这样，您可以通过单击笔记底部的三点菜单在 Keep Web 应用程序上访问它。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="bf7a4db3adb746b886fbfd042443dff9"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Google Keep 的版本历史记录。我看过这方面的新闻，不过写的是“即将推出”。幸运的是，谷歌为我启用了它，这就是它的工作原理。 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Google?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Google</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Android?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Android</a> <a href="https://t.co/MGeCDVz3iM">https://t.co/MGeCDVz3iM</a> <a href="https://t.co/QG12cIlAV5">pic.twitter.com/QG12cIlAV5</a></p> - AssembleDebug (@AssembleDebug) <a href="https://twitter.com/AssembleDebug/status/1692408294521094344?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 18 日</a></blockquote></div><p>正如<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.androidpolice.com/google-keep-finally-gets-version-history-support/"><em><ins>Android Police</ins></em></a>指出的那样，Keep 的版本历史记录目前仅在网络上提供 - 您还无法在 Android 或 iOS 应用程序上看到以前版本的笔记。此外，它不覆盖图像，因此如果您从笔记中删除了照片，您将无法使用此选项恢复它。</p><p>这是一个相当基本的功能，令人困惑的是 Google 直到现在才在 Keep 中提供它。毕竟，该公司长期以来一直在 Google Drive 应用程序中提供类似的功能。实施也很奇怪。与在应用程序中查看版本历史记录并能够通过点击恢复到以前的注释版本（就像您在文档等应用程序中所做的那样）相比，必须下载文件并手动复制文本似乎很奇怪选择。也就是说，这对于 Keep 来说是朝着正确方向迈出的一步。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/google-keep-is-finally-adding-version-history-154441384.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/google-keep-is-finally-adding-version-history-154441384.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 493223f1-38b5-487c-b652-8894fddbaca9</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 18 Aug 2023 15:44:41 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692372891</ingested><modified> 2023-08-18T15:34:54+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Finance Trading]]></category><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Mobile Apps]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="3264" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/d6c147e0-3dda-11ee-bf1e-2a3795a6d391" width="4928"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3264" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/d6c147e0-3dda-11ee-bf1e-2a3795a6d391" width="4928"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[eyecatcher23 via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[red pencil erasing a mistake]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[mistake correction]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best multi-device wireless chargers for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>您很可能拥有足够多支持无线充电的设备，而<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-charger-140036359.html">单个设备垫</a>或支架无法满足您的需求。然而，购买多件无线充电器可能会让人头疼。您不仅需要应对不同程度的支持，还需要应对不同的设计——您最不想要的就是不适合放在床头柜上的东西。 While this space can be confusing, there are plenty of options out there that are worth your money. We&#39;ll walk you through what you need to know to find the best buy while shopping for a multi-device wireless charging station, and recommend a few models that belong on your short list.</p><h2> Future-proofing</h2><p> It won&#39;t be shocking to hear that your smartphone choice influences your choice in a wireless charger. Only iPhone owners will need to consider <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-7-review-all-about-the-screen-130036181.html">Apple Watch</a> compatibility. Likewise, you&#39;ll need an Android phone if you expect to power a <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-watch-4-classic-review-body-fat-scan-wear-os-120026149.html">Galaxy Watch</a> . Buy an iPhone 12 or newer and you can attach your phone magnetically using MagSafe, while the latest Android phones often have some form of fast wireless charging.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> However, it&#39;s not simply a question of getting the fastest charger. You should consider what you might buy in the future. Don&#39;t buy a two-device charger if you have an iPhone and AirPods, but have been eyeing an Apple Watch. And if you think you might switch to an Android cell phone (or vice versa), you&#39;ll want to get something more generic that doesn&#39;t lock you into any one ecosystem.</p><p> Some chargers include cradles, trays and other features that are heavily optimized for particular products, and might not even account for year-to-year changes. Some vertical stands are too tall for small phones like the <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-iphone-13-and-13-mini-review-130035113.html">iPhone 13 mini</a> , for instance. While you can never completely guarantee that next year&#39;s phone or watch will work, it&#39;s worth buying something more likely to last.</p><p> Having said all this, don&#39;t be afraid to get a charger with vendor-specific features if you&#39;re fiercely loyal to one brand. Apple isn&#39;t expected to ditch MagSafe any time soon, and Samsung will likely keep making Galaxy Watches for a while to come.</p><h2> Where and how will you use it? </h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-04/b2b575e0-c7fe-11ec-8ee7-4c395c0c840d" alt="Multi-device wireless charger with Android phone and Samsung earbuds" data-uuid="8fe3128c-11f1-369a-9f1d-d642682e91ad"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Sebastian Bednarek on Unsplash</div></figure><h2></h2><p> Even without a charging cable to worry about, you&#39;re probably buying a multi-device wireless charger with one location in mind. It might sit on your nightstand or on your desk. Not everyone buys a charger just for themselves, though; you might want to use one as a shared station for you and a partner.</p><p> If the charger will sit on your nightstand, you&#39;ll likely want a compact, stable unit that won&#39;t swallow all your free space or tumble to the floor (and if it does fall, one with enough durability to survive). You may also prefer a lay-flat phone pad so your screen is less likely to keep you awake. The Apple Watch and some other smartwatches can double as tiny alarm clocks, so you might want a vertical charging option for any wristwear.</p><p> At a desk, however, you may want a vertical phone stand so you can check notifications. Will the charger sit on a low table? Horizontal charger pads may make it easier to grab your devices in a hurry. Travel chargers should fold up or otherwise protect the pads while they&#39;re in your bag. And, yes, aesthetics count. You may want something pretty if it&#39;s likely to sit in a posh room where guests will see it.</p><p> If it&#39;s a shared charging station, you&#39;ll want something with multiple generic surfaces, and you&#39;ll probably have to forgo charging more than one watch at a time. In those cases, consider the handful of 4-in-1 wireless chargers on the market, or models with USB ports.</p><h2>表现</h2><p>It&#39;s no secret that wireless charging is typically slower than wired, and powering multiple devices adds a new wrinkle. As these chargers often have to support a wide range of hardware, you&#39;ll have to forget about the fastest, device-specific options from brands like Google, OnePlus and Samsung.</p><p> That&#39;s not to say these will be slow, but there just isn&#39;t much separating them on the charging speed front. As a general rule, the quickest multi-device chargers tend to top out at 15W for phones. And you&#39;ll need an Apple MagSafe charger if you want to get that full 15W on an iPhone.</p><p> It&#39;s rare that you&#39;ll find a truly slow example, mind you. Even some of the most affordable options we&#39;ve seen will recharge your phone at a reasonable 7.5W or 10W, and the 5W for other devices is more than enough. If you&#39;re only docking overnight or while you work, speed won&#39;t make a huge difference. Just be sure that whatever you buy is powerful enough for a phone in a case. It&#39;s also worth noting that fast charging for other devices is rare, although you&#39;ll occasionally find speedier options for the Apple Watch Series 7.</p><h2> Quality, box contents and small details </h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-04/225b4f00-c7ff-11ec-935f-08adfbebb3e6" alt="Multi-device wireless charger with iPhone and Apple Watch" data-uuid="54be1cb3-e498-3573-b754-c6262fffaf62"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Melvin Thambi on Unsplash</div></figure><h2></h2><p> The difference between a good charger and a great one often boils down to little details. You won&#39;t always need to pay extra to get those, but a larger outlay may be worthwhile to avoid frustrations for years to come.</p><p> A textured surface like rubberized plastic or fabric will reduce the chances your expensive gadgets will slide off their charging points. The base should have enough grip and weight that the charger won&#39;t easily shift out of place. Any floating or vertical stands should be sturdy — steer clear if there&#39;s any wobble.</p><p> You&#39;ll also want to make a note of what&#39;s included in the box. Some chargers don&#39;t ship with power adapters, and we&#39;ve seen numerous models whose Apple Watch “stands” are merely holders for your existing charging puck.</p><p> Then there&#39;s helpful touches like status lights for confirming correct placement, although you&#39;ll want to make sure they dim or shut off after a certain amount of time. And while it&#39;s still true that cradles and trays can limit compatibility, you do want your devices to stay where you put them. Shelves and lips can prevent your phone or watch from sliding. Oh, and be wary of floating smartwatch mounts, as heavier timepieces might sag.</p><h2> Best premium 3-in-1 charger: Belkin BoostCharge Pro 3-in-1 Wireless Charging Pad with MagSafe </h2><p><core-commerce id="c422ac9621c949f59318b9603e6fcfd3" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> It doesn&#39;t get much better than Belkin&#39;s most advanced model of wireless charger if you&#39;re an Apple devotee. The high-quality <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlXRDlETVFLP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLW80LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI5MmFmY2NhZC03YTZkLTRiM2UtYjcwMS05MWM2MzAxZmQ1MmYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAa3QoFp0ot691Wkn-FBemMxhMyIT_St-bwN8dfxw0bkv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09WD9DMQK%3F">BoostCharge Pro 3-in-1 pad</a> offers 15W MagSafe charging for your iPhone, fast charging for the Apple Watch and a space for AirPods Pro or other earbuds with Qi-compatible cases. The base is weighty, covered in rubberized plastic and includes a discreet status light for your earbuds. More importantly, it supports more devices than you might think. Although the Pro pad uses MagSafe, the horizontal layout lets you charge virtually any phone at reduced speeds. We also have to give Belkin kudos for one of the most convenient Apple Watch chargers we&#39;ve seen. It not only works horizontally and vertically, but includes a knob to adjust for different sizes and third-party cases.</p><p> This is quite large compared to some 3-in-1 chargers, so it&#39;s not the greatest choice for a nightstand. Consider the smaller footprint of its counterpart, the <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9CZWxraW4tTWFnU2FmZS1XaXJlbGVzcy1DaGFyZ2luZy1BcHBsZVdhdGNoL2RwL0IwOFoyWEdIQjM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tbzQtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjkyYWZjY2FkLTdhNmQtNGIzZS1iNzAxLTkxYzYzMDFmZDUyZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAXxirPfhO7Q2cMp_I7BrDxxJec3JwpXzaAMn1uSP4UxQ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBelkin-MagSafe-Wireless-Charging-AppleWatch%2Fdp%2FB08Z2XGHB3">BoostCharge Pro 3-in-1 Wireless Charger</a> with MagSafe 15W, if you have an iPhone 12 or newer. You also won&#39;t find USB ports, and the indented earbud pad rules out a second phone. Still, it&#39;s easily worth the $150 asking price.</p><h2> Runner-up 3-in-1: Logitech Powered 3-in-1 Dock </h2><p><core-commerce id="6b16133cd9f845599468c6042577e49a" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> There are many quality high-end chargers to choose from, but Logitech&#39;s <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXgaqczQ629xUWHFPVMqESeUQ3KhLi_jr7IyFGKs5pPc&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLogitech-950-000015-Powered-3-in-1-Dock%2Fdp%2FB08F4MP3ZJ" class="rapid-with-clickid">Powered 3-in-1 Dock</a> offers a few features that help it rise above. It consumes relatively little space, and the rubberized horizontal and vertical chargers deliver up to 10W while gripping your devices tightly, so both you and your partner can top off.</p><p> It has a few limitations, though. The vertical stand isn&#39;t well-suited to the iPhone 13 mini and other small phones. And while the floating stand works with most Apple Watches, heavier ones tend to sag (such as this author&#39;s steel Series 5 with a Leather Link strap) and might not charge properly. If those aren&#39;t issues, though, your $130 will be well-spent.</p><h2> Best budget 3-in-1 charger: Anker 533 Wireless Charger </h2><p><core-commerce id="267c846e697a4ee9958e5415391990d6" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> You can find plenty of more affordable 3-in-1 chargers. Few, however, offer quite as much for the money as the <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdqv_Motgn20DEsafah-Mrai2P5L17YBsl6kxLBVshNK&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAnker-Magnetic-Wireless-Charging-Station%2Fdp%2FB09CG8P8X5%2F">Anker 533 Wireless Charger 3-in-1 Stand</a> . It offers an adjustable-angle 10W vertical stand and lets you charge an Apple Watch either horizontally or vertically. There&#39;s also a 20W USB-C power adapter in the box, so you won&#39;t have to buy an aftermarket brick (or rely on proprietary cabling) to get started.</p><p> The limitations mostly stem from the cost-cutting measures. You probably won&#39;t have room for a second phone. And like some chargers we&#39;ve seen, the Apple Watch mount is a bring-your-own-cable affair that only supports older USB-A connections. The included cable with your Series 8 or SE won&#39;t work here. At $58, though, this 3-in-1 wireless charging stand is a good bargain.</p><h2> Another good option: Otterbox 3-in-1 Charging Station for MagSafe </h2><p><core-commerce id="5ffff26476974402a50bf3f0bb2f33a8" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> If you&#39;re willing to spend a bit more and live in Apple&#39;s universe, the <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:OtterBox;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=bd89df68-d794-46df-9d47-227b1088ae2b&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=OtterBox&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQjUDI0L2a6vakib3dS2kcEE9vbXDY4njaTrkAUE9uev&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.otterbox.com%2Fen-us%2Fmagsafe-3-in-1-charging-station-for-magsafe-white%2F78-80533.html%3F">Otterbox 3-in-1 Charging Station for MagSafe</a> is worth your attention. The extremely small footprint of this wireless charger is ideal for nightstands. You can tuck a trio of your phone, earbuds and Apple Watch into an area normally reserved for a single device. The company supplies a surprisingly powerful 36W USB-C power adapter in the box that serves as a fast wired option in a pinch.</p><p> The caveats are clear. The floating MagSafe stand rules out Android phones and older iPhones. You&#39;ll need to bring your own Apple Watch cable, and the USB-A port won&#39;t work with the USB-C cables bundled with newer watches. The horizontal-only watch mount also rules out clock functionality. The overall balance of space and utility is still difficult to top for $80.</p><h2> Best 2-in-1 charger: Mophie Dual Wireless Charging Pad </h2><p><core-commerce id="b9ce414474a34d20905c559aa314a7cf" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The 2-in-1 field is highly competitive and makes it difficult to choose an absolute winner. However, <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASPn72Yo5yZgMarHkS1lnYRZXcnsirWkFXP4tGCjTBCF&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FMophie-Dual-Wireless-Charging-Pad%2Fdp%2FB07XPDWZLF">Mophie&#39;s Dual Wireless Charging Pad</a> hits many of the right marks. It can charge two devices at up to 10W each, making it a great pick for a two-phone household. The fabric surface with rubberized trim should keep your gadgets steady, and the status lights will confirm accurate placement. There&#39;s even a USB-A port to plug in your watch charger or any other wired hardware.</p><p> The complaints are few. You won&#39;t charge at 15W, and we&#39;d rather have USB-C than USB-A. It&#39;s nonetheless a safe choice at $80, and worth buying over less expensive options.</p><h2> Runner-up 2-in-1: Samsung Super Fast Wireless Charger Duo </h2><p><core-commerce id="cf5bfe1d2e994809a81eb069fd46c3e3" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Multi-device chargers from phone manufacturers tend to be either compromised or highly proprietary, but <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdp0xhzFkGRaXjZnx_06GxSuHP-iXe7fZfM_69pEIgpT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSamsung-Wireless-Universally-Compatible-Included%2Fdp%2FB09MV3BRHC">Samsung&#39;s Super Fast Wireless Charger Duo</a> (sometimes known as the 15W Duo Fast Wireless Charger) bucks that trend. It&#39;s compact and delivers high-speed charging for one phone and an accessory, whether it&#39;s a Samsung Galaxy Watch or another manufacturer&#39;s earbuds. The status lights will even dim at night, and change color to indicate when your batteries are full.</p><p> This won&#39;t help for two-phone households, and Samsung only guarantees 15W charging for some of its own phones (the Galaxy Note 10, Galaxy S20 and later). You&#39;ll also want to be mindful of which version you buy, as there are variants with and without a power adapter in the box. Neither is cheap at respective prices of $90 and $70. This remains an elegant charger for nightstands and travel, though, and the pads are sufficiently device-agnostic.</p><h2> Best charger for two people: Mophie 4-in-1 Wireless Charging Mat </h2><p><core-commerce id="509860c294474697bbae89e077746a36" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> There are few wireless chargers built with more than one person in mind, but <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9XaXJlbGVzcy1DaGFyZ2luZy1tYXQtd2lyZWxlc3NseS1BZGRpdGlvbmFsL2RwL0IwOExLR1FMUkM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tbzQtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjkyYWZjY2FkLTdhNmQtNGIzZS1iNzAxLTkxYzYzMDFmZDUyZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZ5e7GevxI0uXArUjmoMYikNnbxzdKC1iijnNp-ORzaU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FWireless-Charging-mat-wirelessly-Additional%2Fdp%2FB08LKGQLRC">Mophie&#39;s 4-in-1 Wireless Charging Mat</a> is the most well-rounded of the bunch. The pad can handle up to four devices wirelessly at 10W, including two phones and two accessories. There&#39;s also a spare USB-A port for charging earlier Apple Watch models (using the included mount and your own cable) or wired items. A fabric surface, subtle device trays and indicator lights will also take the mysteries out of charging.</p><p> This is a giant charger compared to most, and you might find it limiting if your home has more than one Apple Watch or accessories that won&#39;t fit the smaller charging pads. Even so, Mophie is offering considerable value for $150. The 4-in-1 does more than some 3-in-1 chargers at that price, and it doesn&#39;t suffer the compatibility issues of rivals like Nomad&#39;s Base Station Pro.</p><p></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-multi-device-wireless-chargers-130020900.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-multi-device-wireless-chargers-130020900.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 92afccad-7a6d-4b3e-b701-91c6301fd52f</guid><dc:creator> Jon Fingas</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 18 Aug 2023 15:32:41 +